name: Snailhenge - cover
description:
The great and mighty Snailhenge.

The magnificence of this structure attracted many viewers of the shelled variety. They gawked at the construction, only something a god might manage.

The historical documentation of this ancient wonder will be released over time as a series. The art piece existed in physical form, created by the author of the NFT, a true original both in the physical world and the digital.
